name: Uyun The Infinite Tunnel
description: While sailing in the Ocean of Desires, Dino falls into the trap of Uyun. This Multi-eyed spirit appears every 300 years in Yajur, the third Magical Location, and is one of the 5 mythical beasts of this world. The only way for Dino to continue his adventure is to go through the infinite tunnel inside Uyun’s body and experience all of his worst fears. Dino has no other choice; this challenge will only make him stronger. Unlocking this portal will increase your Courage Attribute by 550 MPs.
